var merged = objects.reduce(union); // =>{x:1,y:2,z:3}
```

例2：统计字符串中每个字符出现的重复次数

```js
var arr = 'abcdabcdadbc';
var info = arr.split('').reduce((p,k) => (p[k]++ || (p[k] = 1), p), {});
